title: [Dabbings Mews, Twisty Alley]
description: The cold alley twists out of sight, winding between closely set buildings.  Delectable aromas of pastries baking scent the frosty air, so strong and tangible, they seem almost visible.  Halflings hurry by each other with purposeful strides, shoulders brushing in the confined avenue.
tags: meta:mapname:Neighborhoods of Icemule Trace and Pinefar
